== 獎項 ==
此劇在2002年的[[英國學術電視獎|英國學術電視獎]]獲得最佳劇情電視劇、最佳設計和最佳化妝獎等，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.es/books?id=kW8j6sHvrewC&pg=PA635&lpg=PA635&dq=The+Way+We+Live+Now+British+Academy+Television+Awards&source=bl&ots=UzxQwYq-AZ&sig=c6G2QD5sPSSSqFaGcCWLqlwbvBQ&hl=es&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj4t7SqwprRAhVGJcAKHXtOBGYQ6AEISzAG#v=onepage&q=The%20Way%20We%20Live%20Now%20British%20Academy%20Television%20Awards&f=false|title=''Encyclopedia of Television Film Directors'': DAVID YATES|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203021227/https://books.google.es/books?id=kW8j6sHvrewC&pg=PA635&lpg=PA635&dq=The+Way+We+Live+Now+British+Academy+Television+Awards&source=bl&ots=UzxQwYq-AZ&sig=c6G2QD5sPSSSqFaGcCWLqlwbvBQ&hl=es&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj4t7SqwprRAhVGJcAKHXtOBGYQ6AEISzAG#v=onepage&q=The%20Way%20We%20Live%20Now%20British%20Academy%20Television%20Awards&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[大衛·蘇歇|大衛·蘇歇]]提名最佳演員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bricksite.com/davidsuchet?id=31543|title=David Suchet: Awards and nominations|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203021222/https://www.bricksite.com/davidsuchet?id=31543|dead-url=no}}</ref>

